      "content": "hey so im 20 weeks pregnant and my sinuses are like super clogged and hurting so bad i cant even sleep. i have some ciprofloxacin left over from a different infection a few months ago... is it okay if i just take a few of those to clear this up? i really dont wanna make a doctor's appointment if i dont have to",
