      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should probably check but i'm just so tired of feeling like this. is ciprofloxacin really that bad for the baby? i mean it's just a few pills to get me through the night. i've heard people take antibiotics during pregnancy all the time to avoid getting sicker so i'm a bit confused why this one is different.",
